videos.headline: Ball State on the board with rush TD
videos.description: Ball State running back Malik Dunner takes the toss untouched to the end zone for the Cardinals' first points.

videos.headline: WKU QB fools defense with triple-option TD toss
videos.description: Western Kentucky quarterback Steven Duncan fakes out the Ball State defense on a triple-option touchdown toss to Mik'Quan Deane.

videos.headline: Ball State back on top with 6-yard TD
videos.description: Ball State wide receiver Corey Lacanaria sneaks in between two blockers on the bubble-screen reception and walks in a 6-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Duncan finds Deane again for 6
videos.description: Western Kentucky quarterback Steven Duncan lofts an 18-yard touchdown to Mik'Quan Deane, their second scoring connection of the game.
